comments:
Created 1.4.1987 out of the parishes of Horsham Rural, 
    Slinford and Warnham. See also Table 2, note (l).

Created 1.4.1987 out of the parishes of Horsham Rural, Lower 
    Beeding and Rusper. See also Table 2, note (l).

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Crawley unparished area. See also Table 
    2, notes (e), (i) and (j).

Abolished 1.4.1974 to become an unparished area. See also Table 
    2, note (d).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish of Horsham. See also Table 2, note 
    (l).

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Horsham. 
    Abolished 1.4.1987 and added to the Horsham unparished area and the 
    parishes of Broadbridge Heath, Colgate, Itchingfield, North Horsham, 
    Nuthurst, Rusper, Slinfold, Southwater and Warnham.
Abolished 1.4.1933 and added to the parish of Crawley.

Created 1.4.1987 out of the Horsham unparished area and part 
    of the parish of Horsham Rural. See also Table 2, note (l).

Created 1.4.1987 out of the parishes of Horsham Rural and 
    Itchingfield. See also Table 2, note (l).
